Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:56.05,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\an8}The city of Pompeii was considered a peaceful, \N prosperous health resort by the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:05.77,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,It was destroyed in an instant by ash and lava from \N the sudden eruption of Mt. Vesuvius on August 24th, 79 AD. {no one knows wtf lapilli is, and lapilli particles less than 2mm are ash, which was the main contributor to the destruction and preservation of Pompeii}{should we add a second "was" for good measure?}{yes -J}{and just to be extra spicy, a third}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.61,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Archaeologists later discovered that \N all the houses, streets, bottles of wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:16.11,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,...and even tracks left by carriages had been perfectly preserved \N as they were when the volcano erupted 1,800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:24.58,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,The dog mosaic we're looking for is located near \N the entrance of the House of the Tragic Poet {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/House_of_the_Tragic_Poet}in Pompeii.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.33,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Oh, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.84,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You were supposed to turn right \N at that intersection, not left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.64,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You should have spoken up sooner, Giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.81,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What use is it telling me to turn right \N after I already went the wrong way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.85,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.81,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. \N I'll be more careful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.73,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You're missing my point, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.53,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hey, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.61,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We're in a hurry, so keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.74,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I'm well aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:06.29,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\an8}For fuck's sake... {This was commented out for the TV airing, but I commented it back in since it's fairly audible. Feel free to comment it back out if you disagree. -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.08,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Well, I expected nothing less of Fugo.{HLTL is more like "Well, Fugo's his usual self..." -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:12.88,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,My real concern is the new guy, \N Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:16.96,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll treat him like the others \N since that's what Buccellati told me to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:22.51,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but something about him \N rubs me the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.85,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He's gonna fuck things up sooner or later...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.52,Thoughts,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Probably get us all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.23,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Pompeii, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.15,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I took a field trip here as a kid. \N Haven't been back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.16,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, Giorno, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.29,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,The place we're looking for \N is a hundred meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:58.50,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,It should take us about thirty minutes \N to find what we need and regroup with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.64,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, Giorno, stay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.14,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,To think we'd be found so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.52,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,How many we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.15,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,One. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.94,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,He's peeking around the stone pillar behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.99,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Pillar? Which one do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.86,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Giorno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.86,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,There's only one pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.53,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Can't you see it from that angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.87,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo, it's true there's only one pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.21,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but I don't see anyone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.00,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Quit messing around! \N He's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:38.67,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.76,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,There! \N That guy walking toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.30,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,H-He was right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.97,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,A man came out from behind the pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.35,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I saw him in the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.39,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.40,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,There! He's right there! \N He's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.82,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,H-He's inside the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.74,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,He revealed his Stand! \N Who's fighting him? {Which of us will fight him?}{Entire line needs to be short -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.95,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hold on, Fugo! \N I still don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.75,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.00,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,This is bad! \N He's about to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.71,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Get away from the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.88,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.84,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Giorno! Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.72,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Wh-Where did you go? \N Giorno? Abbacchio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.89,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.35,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,The man in the mirror is gone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.81,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.57,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,A mirror hanging in a place like this \N was bizarre to begin with! {HE SAID THE THING}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.95,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What even is this ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.78,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.49,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is... {OH MY GOD THEY SPELLED "TRASH" BACKWARDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.37,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,...but something about the scenery feels off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.33,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.21,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.76,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Pannacotta Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:12.72,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Possesses an IQ of 152 which earned him \N{allowed him\N to enter} admission into university at the age of thirteen.{HLTL: Said to possess high intelligence with an IQ of 152, he was admitted into university at age thirteen.}{I suppose we can afford to miss the "high intelligence" bit since 152 is implied to be high, but it might not be a bad idea to rewrite the line if others feel this isn't obvious. Also something else to consider: Should this and the next few lines read closer to a report, i.e. minimal pronouns? -JMFW}{I like this line as it is, but leaving the comments for others to go over -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:19.40,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,During his time there, he lost his temper with a professor, \N assaulting him with a four-kilogram encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.23,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,This sent him into an \N unending downward spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:27.24,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,He is accompanied by \N ex-police officer Leone Abbacchio, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.45,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Nothing on the other guy. \N Must be new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.99,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I believe I heard the name Giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.75,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,What did you do to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.66,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Y-You scumbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.12,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.38,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,The watch numbers are backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.80,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,And now it's on my \N right wrist instead of my left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.31,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! \N This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.43,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Your ability is{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.39,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,As I predicted, you figured it out quickly. {SASUGA ILLUSO-SAN -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.98,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I'll take you all out one by one, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.32,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who goes first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:08.03,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,...but I'll start with you, \N since you looked in the mirror first. {comma}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.11,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Abbacchio and Giorno weren't \N the ones who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.57,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I-I'm inside the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.91,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.83,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I'm the one who was dragged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.67,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo! {FYUUGO}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.33,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Where are you, Fugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.09,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hey, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.55,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Did you see something or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.71,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.68,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It looked to me as though \N he suddenly disappeared, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.68,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.52,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Before he disappeared, \N Fugo yelled at us to get away from the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.19,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He also asked us whether we could see \N a man coming out from behind a pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,This mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.48,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Is there something going on... \N with this mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.70,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,The question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.95,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,...where are you hiding the boss's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.37,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Well, that's the most \N {\i1}important{\i0} question, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:07.34,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I should also probably figure out what the three of you \N are doing here in Pompeii, the city of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:11.34,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I suppose you're here \N looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:16.43,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,If that's the case, \N you came here to {pick up}get something you need to protect the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.47,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:22.35,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,If you turn left up ahead, \N you'll arrive at the famous dog mosaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.48,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Is there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.40,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.15,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.11,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Tell me what you're looking for, Fugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.11,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I refuse! {aww snap}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.90,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.12,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.66,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You're the one who's going to die \N after witnessing my ability! {literally no u}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.54,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Purple Haze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.00,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,My Stand isn't appearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:52.09,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I see... \N So your Stand is named Purple Haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.22,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,Something's wrong. \N I definitely called out my Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:01.02,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,I can feel it... so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.44,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hey, Giorno...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.44,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Slowly walk toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.48,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Slowly what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.61,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Just get the fuck over here, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.74,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fuck going slow! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.20,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What?! Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.20,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Giorno! Ignore that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.91,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's not our enemy! \N That's Fugo's Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.33,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Now hurry and get the fuck away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.87,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Don't get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Fugo's{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.88,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Get the hell away from Purple Haze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.96,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.10,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,You're currently inside the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:46.73,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can figure out why \N I dragged you in here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:54.19,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,If I had brought anyone else in who could fight me, \N I'd be in deep shit! {jankk}{I dunno how to fix D: -J}{fuck you past me this shit ain't nothing. fool. -J}{you still suck though -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:58.16,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I control what's inside the mirror... \N That's my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:02.08,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Everything in here is a lifeless object.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.79,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,You and I are the only living inhabitants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.37,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I intentionally haven't let anyone else in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.88,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I only allowed your physical body inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:15.38,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,In other words... \N Your Stand ability was left outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.47,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,This is my Man in the Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.14,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,Purple Haze materialized \N outside of the mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.77,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,With that in mind, \N there must be a way I can fight this!
Comment: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:47.00,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Pannacotta Fugo was born into a wealthy family \N who owned a large estate in the suburbs of Naples. {"a large property" sounds a little weird, but this isn't a change I'm married to. -JMFW}{I like this but will keep comments for others to check -Gyro}{"Parcel" was also weird to me. Changed to "estate" on Jules's suggestion. -TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:54.55,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,In addition to being born into a life of luxury, \N he was gifted with great intelligence, possessing an IQ of 152.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:58.63,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He appeared to have \N a perfect life on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:08.39,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the weight of the expectations his parents \N and others placed on him slowly began to crush his young heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:17.15,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,At times, Fugo would experience fits of rage \N that even he himself couldn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...but he did everything in his power \N to control them and get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:32.58,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Later on, after entering university at the age of thirteen, \N his rage manifested in the worst way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.96,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,Fugo, lad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.34,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.51,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,What are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.47,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I'm working on the assignment due next week. \N I can't find any good former cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.85,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,Oh, come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:51.89,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,I already told you to come to me \N if there was anything you didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.48,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't want to be \N constantly bothering you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:12:00.78,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,It's my job to educate and lead \N young people like you in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.45,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.53,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,Why don't you come by \N my house again for dinner, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.99,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.33,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,Now, wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:14.21,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,If you like, I suppose I could tell you \N what will be on the next test...{"...agete mo ii" is a relatively common term in Japanese and while it LITERALLY translates to "I don't mind doing..." I feel like that isn't really an expression used in English. Nowhere near as common, at least. -Starfish}{We use the expression, but here it'd be tweaked to "I don't mind telling..." -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.63,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,It will be fine. Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.63,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBABABA&}Stop it... Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.59,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Stop it. Stop it. Stop it. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.59,Flashback,Creep,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBABABA&}I'll be nice and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.01,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I told you to stop, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.72,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I always looked up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.60,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,You fucking piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.14,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.31,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Apparently Fugo got real friendly \N with one of the professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.11,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You sure he wasn't the one leading him on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.36,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Probably "charmed" his way \N through the entrance exam, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.20,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Fugo's parents used their wealth \N to ensure he wasn't found guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:54.62,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...but they treated him \N like filth and disowned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:59.88,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,With nowhere to turn,\N Fugo began shoplifting and pickpocketing to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:05.93,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Ironically, this lifestyle encouraged him \N to use his intellect to its fullest potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.89,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You little shit! \N You trying to dine and dash on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.89,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna throw your ass in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.94,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,No, I won't be going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:19.36,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with \N De Sica{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vittorio_De_Sica} v. Argento{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dario_Argento}{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nastro_d%27Argento} from 1982{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenebrae_(film)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:26.07,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Since precedent will be taken into account,{And here we have the second use of "hanrei", the one and only resource I can think of for the previous scene. -Starfish} \N the court will likely rule that I was acting out of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.24,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Mr. Buccellati! \N Please say something to this brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.25,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:41.09,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,This was around the time when Buccellati \N was thinking about forming his own team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.30,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,So that's my life story, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.22,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Please don't take pity on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.60,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I don't see my situation as unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:55.77,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Of course. \N But, hmm... I feel our meeting here is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.36,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Would you like to join my team, \N Pannacotta Fugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.73,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,I want your knowledge and intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.36,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Mr. Buccellati, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.49,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Joining a gang doesn't sound so bad, \N but I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.79,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I'm going to live on my own, and keep{ing} to myself. {and keep}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.25,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.91,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.46,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,When I lose my temper, I do horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.51,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,If I were to join your team, \N I could end up killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.22,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Well then, let's see if that {will}comes to pass. {"If that's all" reads a little odd here. More like "Well then, [...]" -JMFW}{applied Jules' suggestion -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.43,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Come with me, Fugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:37.43,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll bring out the best in you. \N Your fierce, impulsive rage and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.19,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,These words moved Fugo's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:48.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After that, Fugo took Polpo's test \N and gained Purple Haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.57,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,So this is Fugo's Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:56.08,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Fugo isn't here, \N yet for some reason his Stand appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:00.96,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo's probably doing all right for now \N since this thing is here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.54,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Dammit! \N Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.34,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,How is he protecting himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.13,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Stay back, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.51,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Even more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.30,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Fugo doesn't let this thing out very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.64,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It only happens when he's in deep shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.77,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,This has gotta mean \N Fugo's trying to fight somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.19,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You're still too close, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:27.40,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He seems more worried about \N that Stand than where Fugo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.28,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,He feels threatened.{He's acting threatened.}{Eh... Not really loving this wording. Literal is "He has an attitude of feeling threatened" which is of course worse, but even the edit feels a bit clunky to me. -Starfish}{Reworked the line. Think this is about what GioGio means -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.37,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What's going on? \N It started attacking out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.04,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,This is really bad! \N We need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.71,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We're leaving! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.25,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.29,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,There's something in that mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.79,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We need to find Fugo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.00,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's the most important thing right{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.05,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Don't talk back to me, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.63,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I don't give a fuck what happens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.85,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but I'm telling you since you clearly have \N no idea what the fuck is going on!{JP has "I'm kindly telling you" but I guess this line is pushing the CPS already and adding another word would bring it up to 20 which is... a thing best avoided if possible. -Starfish} {I don't think I have a way to feasibly bring down character count while retaining meaning... much as it pains me, I think we're going to have a casualty of translation -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.35,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It punched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.56,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Run, Giorno! {Giorno was a maaaaan who thought he was a loner, but he knew it wouldn't last}{rare Giorno}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.81,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.52,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,So you activated{Note that even in Japanese he uses a different word here than they normally do. -Starfish} your Stand \N outside the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.11,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,But... it won't mean shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.78,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how \N your Stand uses its ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.58,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,It will never be able to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.17,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,But I can beat you to death \N whenever I feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.75,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,A crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.17,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Why did a crow suddenly just fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.76,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,A crow just fell out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.35,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.98,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Whoever's in Purple Haze's way \N better move when it starts swinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.98,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,What the hell is with these corpses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.78,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's a killer virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.58,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's Fugo's Stand, Purple Haze's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.37,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,A virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.54,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Look at its hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.17,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,After its fist connects with something, \N one of the capsules breaks open...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.63,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...and the virus comes spilling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:16.51,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The virus goes airborne \N and enters the body through inhalation or skin contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.72,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Then it rapidly multiplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.10,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It infects its host within thirty seconds, \N then instantly kills them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:29.11,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,And once the virus spreads, \N it doesn't matter who's nearby, be it friend or foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:32.57,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Just like those crows, \N all of your bodily functions will shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.65,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...and you'll die as you rot from the inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.28,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That includes your Stand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.87,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What's its range?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.24,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Five meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:45.91,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Right now, Fugo should be controlling his Stand \N within five meters of his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:49.13,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's obviously important, \N but what's the range of the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.88,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,How close do you have to be to get infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.63,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We should be safe from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:18:01.81,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The virus inside its capsules dies within \N a few dozen seconds of being exposed to normal indoor light. {as in that species (?) of virus dies within a few dozen seconds}{viruses come in strains}{The mitocondria is the powerhouse of the cell}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:06.27,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,The crows' corpses should be \N sterilized by the sunlight soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.27,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:14.36,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It strikes like an explosion, \N then scatters like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.99,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It's a Stand which personifies Fugo's violent nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.58,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.62,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I think it's trying to wipe off \N the drool that dripped on its leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:33.55,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It always looks pissed off, \N but it's really compulsive and cares about cleanliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.80,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You could say it's a Stand of habit. {ba dum tish?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.65,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,His Stand doesn't seem to possess \N much intelligence, if any...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:59.20,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,That's because it's a reflection \N of his angry side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:04.24,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It also proves that Fugo \N can't see Purple Haze right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.58,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He doesn't have it under control at all. {Keep consistent with 289 -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.62,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,He'd never let it act like this if he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.75,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,This corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.67,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,This crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.21,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Was it sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.42,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Was it infected by some virus or bacteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.48,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I knew it... \N Fugo doesn't have it under control!{Same phrasaing as 283 -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.57,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,It attacked another random spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.24,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,Wait, was that actually random?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.11,Thoughts,Giorno,0,0,0,,There must be something in the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.28,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,So now you attacked the mirror from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.08,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,But that was pointless, Fugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.33,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,That was a normal mirror \N like you could find anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.04,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,No matter what your Stand \N does on the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.92,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of ability it has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:59.92,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Not even viruses can enter \N the world of Man in the Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:04.47,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,Abbacchio, Giorno, please get my message...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.39,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,Please don't let yourselves \N be dragged into the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.81,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We need to hurry, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.40,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Hey, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.69,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Let me ask you this... \N Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.20,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,To retrieve the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.62,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,You're willing to abandon Fugo \N while he's in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.83,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:39.84,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Listen here. We were ordered to retrieve the key \N and safely bring the girl to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.18,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I want to save Fugo \N just as much as you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.43,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...but retrieving the key is our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.77,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Even if I were the one being \N attacked right now and not Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.89,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,...I'd want you guys to abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.19,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I don't mean to be rude... {"You smell nice."}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.36,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...but I disagree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:02.15,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Fugo may be in grave danger, \N but it isn't like he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.74,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We should risk our lives to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:09.28,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,Besides, making another move before we know the enemy's ability puts us at risk, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.62,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,No! The worst thing we could possibly do \N is risk all three of us being taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.08,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I'll say it again! \N We're moving on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.33,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,I respectfully refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.34,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,We will solve this mystery, \N rescue Fugo, then defeat the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.67,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,That's the only way to ensure our safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.22,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,I have seniority here, \N so we're doing things my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.05,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You sure you still refuse? {no, now kiss}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.60,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,You're gonna have hell to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.56,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,If somehow you survive, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.99,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I'll ask you once more, Fugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.70,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,What are you looking for here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.24,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,I've no intention of telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.20,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.75,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,Very well. \N There's always the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.17,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,I just need the last one standing to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:02.17,Main,Illuso,0,0,0,,You're finished! Take this!
